Metadata: New isoeudistomin class dihydro-​beta-​carbolines from an undescribed ascidian of the genus "Eudistoma"

19-​Bromoisoeudisto​min U (1) and isoeudistomin U (2), two new dihydro-​beta-​carbolines have been isolated from an undescribed Western Australian ascidian of the genus "Eudistoma". Their structures were determined by comprehensive spectral analyses primarily involving 2D NMR.
